{"tid":448414,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救] Display卡唔知係咪壞左","createTime":"2017-10-26T07:50:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T11:36:10.000Z","uid":78282,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1446a204986634227c6c072ec07c9d6e963a199f","tid":448414,"uid":78282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:50:53.000Z","msg":"琴晚無息機 今朝開翻mon 就黑左screen 無野睇<br />\n開機去到windows個icon之後就變全黑<br />\n<br />\n跟住重機 開左安全模式入既話 個mon係work既<br />\n跟住del左舊drivers, 裝左個新既 <br />\n重機都係黑mon<br />\n<br />\n之後我set左用standard vga果個做display<br />\n就著得翻mon<br />\n<br />\n用緊AMD r9 200<br />\n其實係咪張野壞左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早幾日都有類似情況但係重機多幾次就無事<br />\n今日好似收左皮<br />\n<br />\n求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bcf5c649085d96ef7d6b927c31eb251f23942e2","tid":448414,"uid":78282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T08:09:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc1b89ce3fba88859a59b287981df510324384d","tid":448414,"uid":127123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T08:40:23.000Z","msg":"清塵,刷銅片重插卡果D基本野試過未?"},{"pid":"5343d17acb7928dbc4c5d63238bfb910994b3e1b","tid":448414,"uid":78282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T08:51:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>清塵,刷銅片重插卡果D基本野試過未?</blockquote><br />\n未 而家試下"},{"pid":"f94df0f62270dc033d30aa570792153721696d65","tid":448414,"uid":155485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T08:52:18.000Z","msg":"其實會唔會關新版drivers事?<br />\n我有試過類似既情況"},{"pid":"87470f58e8d3cc3