,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T11:33:50.000Z","msg":"更新過DRIVER?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係既話.有機會炒左DRIVER<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n死DISPLAY個人經驗通常花畫面多"},{"pid":"20e7e379df511ba511214816664bb76bc7165814","tid":448414,"uid":67338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T11:36:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>down display driver uninstaller, del嗮display driver, 熄機拆display卡<br />\n用返onboard display冇事就係display 壞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n試過NVIDIA CARD都炒DRIVER.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n頂佢個掣.已經預先行原廠UNINSTALLER刪左舊版先.都係BOOT唔番入WINDOWS.一上DRIVER就入唔到WINDOWS,用哂DRIVER SWEEPER都唔得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後搞到要刪機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}